<A>__{margaret walks up the center of main street toward the camera with her books pressed against her chest. she passes the drugstore, then the hardware store ... far off in the distance, a young man comes racing out of the soda shop, pulling off his little paper hat as he goes. he comes running up behind her as fast as he can.}
<B>__{closer.}
<A>__{he takes a deep breath and tries to quiet the panting.}
<C>__{david}
<D>__{hi.}
<C>__{margaret}
